[section Overview]
As NT2 scope and coverage grows, the validation of NT2 API is critical
and require specific testing facilities like being able to report errors in
type computation or numerical precision divergence. This module provides macros,
classes and functions to setup, write and run unit tests for any NT2 module.
[endsect]

[h2 Dependencies]
NT2.Test.Unit depends on the following components:

* NT2 Configuration
* NT2 Error Handling
* NT2 SIMD SDK

